– Spain and France oppose the suspension of aid to the occupied Palestinian territories;
– The Israeli Air Force urgently sent planes to Europe to gather Israelis for military service living there and send them to Israel;
– The UN condemns the total blockade of Gaza.

‼️ Brief overview of recent events:

– Israel continued bombing Gaza throughout the night, striking residential buildings. In total, more than 200 houses were affected;
– The death toll now stands at 704 Palestinians in the Gaza Strip, more than 900 in Israel, at least 17 Palestinians in the occupied West Bank and four Hezbollah fighters in Lebanon;
– The UN humanitarian agency reported that more than 187,518 Palestinians had fled their homes in Gaza, with more than 137,000 taking refuge in 84 schools;
– The Israeli military offered Palestinians fleeing air attacks in the Gaza Strip to go to Egypt, which also borders the blocked enclave. After some time, information appeared about the closure of the checkpoint on the Egyptian border;
– The IDF announced the killing of about 1,500 Hamas militants, and it was also announced that government buildings in Gaza are a “legitimate target” for Israeli strikes;
– The Israeli blockade of Gaza is considered a war crime under UN statutes;

• 50% of Russian believes that in the treatment of the same disease, official medicine is more effective, another 40% think that somewhere official is more effective, and somewhere folk;
• 47% turn to a doctor in case of illness and are treated only with prescribed medications, one in three uses traditional medicine methods in addition to prescribed medications (32%);
• 71% practice traditional medicine. The survey was conducted by All-Russian Center for the Study of Public Opinion (VTsIOM).

Folk medicine is used by citizens in cases when the official one is either too expensive or does not inspire confidence, since it has long turned into a simple set of goods and services. Plus idealistic delusions, whose adherents reject the achievements of modern science. Under the capitalist system, medicine balances between maintaining the health of the workforce for subsequent exploitation and such "health care" that life expectancy does not increase too much (pensions for the elderly are "unnecessary" expenses).

Conscription up to 30 years and the strengthening of the militarization of the economy in Russia are the main amendments to the second reading of the draft law on military age:

— The upper limit of the draft age will grow to 30 years immediately and without a transition period – according to the plan, the new limits (18-30 years) will start working on January 1, 2024.

— Regions by the decision of the president during the period of martial law and mobilization will be able to create unitary enterprises to help the security forces;

— Specialized enterprises to ensure security and combat saboteurs will be able to receive small arms.

— Conscripts are allowed to enter into contracts for military service for a year during the period of mobilization and under martial law;

Brief summary:

– After Prigozhin’s statements on the evening of June 23, the Wagner leadership is located in Rostov, along with the leadership of the RF Armed Forces;

- Both groups are trying to appeal to the support of the people: after Putin's speech, in which Wagner mercenaries were equated with the workers and peasants of 1917, officials condemned the rebellion and are currently "defending the constitutional order." Prigozhin claims that his actions are aimed at achieving "justice";

– It is known about clashes between the RF Armed Forces and Wagner PMC in the Voronezh region;

– There is practically no reaction from foreign states; it is known about the negotiations of Putin with the leaders of the CIS countries.

We remind you that regardless of the outcome of current events, ordinary citizens will be the losers. Communists must refrain from spontaneous thoughtless actions and continue the work of building a unified communist organization.

In an emergency newscast on Channel One Russia, the news anchor repeated the earlier statements of the Ministry of Defense and a number of Telegram channels, stating that:

- video of the strike on Prigozhin's mercenaries - is a staging;

- Prigozhin's statements were prepared in advance;

- The Ministry of Defense denies the strike on Wagner.

According to estimates published in the British magazine 'The Economist', the Russian Federation is facing a real demographic catastrophe. Namely:

Average life expectancy for men aged 15 and over has fallen to the level of Haiti (to 64.2 years). Considering that the retirement age in the Russian Federation for men is now 65;

The female population exceeds the male population by 10 million people;

People in Russia die 6 years earlier than in Bangladesh and 18 years earlier than in Japan;

In the last 3 years, the country has lost 2 million more people than it used to due to disease, military conflicts and migration.

